{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-24","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 24","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Nakon neuređene liste, dodaj novu sliku sa vrednošću <code>src</code> atributa postavljenom na:</p>\n<p><code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg</code></p>\n<p>I sa vrednošću <code>alt</code> atributa postavljenom na:</p>\n<p><code>A slice of lasagna on a plate.</code></p>\n</section>","id":"5dfb6250eacea3f48c6300b2","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-24"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        \n      </section>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[18,20],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Imaj <code>img</code> element odmah nakon završne oznake <code>&#x3C;/ul></code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(document.querySelectorAll('section')[1]?.querySelector('ul').nextElementSibling?.nodeName, 'IMG');"},{"text":"<p>Nova slika nema atribut polja <code>alt</code>. Proverite da postoji razmak nakon imena oznake otvaranja i/ili da postoji razmak pre svih imena atributa polja.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelectorAll('section')[1]?.querySelector('ul').nextElementSibling?.hasAttribute('alt'));"},{"text":"<p>Nova slika treba da ima vrednost atributa <code>alt</code> <code>A slice of lasagna on a plate.</code>. Uverite se da je vrednost atributa <code>alt</code> okružena navodnicima.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\n  document.querySelectorAll('section')[1]?.querySelector('ul').nextElementSibling?.getAttribute('alt')?.replace(/\\s+/g, ' '), /^A slice of lasagna on a plate\\.?$/i \n);"},{"text":"<p>Nova slika nema atribut elementa <code>src</code>. Proverite da postoji razmak nakon naziva otvarajuće oznake i/ili da postoji razmak pre svih imena atributa elemenata.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelectorAll('section')[1]?.querySelector('ul').nextElementSibling?.hasAttribute('src'));"},{"text":"<p>Nova slika treba da ima vrednost atributa <code>src</code> <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg</code>. Uverite se da je vrednost atributa <code>src</code> okružena navodnicima.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(\n  document.querySelectorAll('section')[1]?.querySelector('ul').nextElementSibling?.getAttribute('src'),\n    'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg'\n);"},{"text":"<p>Iako si postavio <code>src</code> atribut nove slike na ispravan URL, uvek se preporučuje da vrednosti atributa okružiš navodnicima.</p>","testString":"assert.notMatch(code, /\\<img\\s+.+\\s+src\\s*=\\s*https:\\/\\/cdn\\.freecodecamp\\.org\\/curriculum\\/cat-photo-app\\/lasagna\\.jpg/);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/#workshop-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-24","certification":"responsive-web-design-v9","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","chapter":"html","module":"basic-html","block":"workshop-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-25","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-23","id":"5dfb6250eacea3f48c6300b2","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-24"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}